title: Recall Notification Report 033-2014 (Boneless Skinless Chicken Breasts)
summary: WASHINGTON, May 29, 2014 Boulder Natural Meats, a Denver, Colo., establishment, is recalling approximately 363 pounds of Boneless Skinless Chicken Breasts due to misbranding, the U.S. Department of Agriculture's Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today. The product was formulated with wheat, which is...
impacted_products: 1 to 1.5-lbs. vacuum sealed packages of  “Boneless Skinless Chicken Breasts brushed with Teriyaki Seasoning”
